###############################################################################
#				Tic Tac Toe: With the Big Three
# I. Python
# =========
# Install Python:
# 	1. http://www.python.org/getit/
# 	2. Add Folder to Path (Example: C:\Python3#\)
#
# Source Example:
#	1. http://www.cs.indiana.edu/classes/a202-dger/spr2007/notes/code/chap06/tic-tac-toe.py
#		a. Have to convert "raw_input" to "input"; print "<stuff>" to print("<stuff>")
#
# Building/Execution: (trick!--python is compiled at runtime)
#	1. Run: python <name>.py

# II. Java
# ========
# Install Java:
#	1. http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/jdk7-downloads-1880260.html
#	2. Add jdk to Path, OR change the directory to the binary folder (ex: C:\<java path>\bin\) (See other instructions on PATH)
#
# Source Example:
#	1. http://forum.codecall.net/topic/43209-java-source-code-tic-tac-toe-game/
#
# Building/Execution
# 	1. Compile: javac TicTacToe.java (javac <source name>.java)
#	2. Make a jar: jar cvfe TicTacToe.jar TicTacToe TicTacToe.class (jar <flags> <output name>.jar <default classpath> <files to shove in jar ... >)
#	3. Run: java -jar TicTacToe
#
# (note: This version has a GUI but NO AI!)
# (note: A Step by Step tutorial exists: http://www.instructables.com/id/Make-Tic-Tac-Toe-in-Java/)

# III. C/C++
# ==========
# Install C Compiler (GCC):
# 	1. Windows: Install MinGW (it's GCC, that includes gcc.exe and g++.exe for windows!) -- http://sourceforge.net/projects/mingw/files/Installer/mingw-get-inst/mingw-get-inst-20120426/mingw-get-inst-20120426.exe/download
# 	2a. Linux(Apt): sudo apt-get install build-essential
# 	2b. Linux(Yum): sudo yum groupinstall 'Development Tools'
# 	3. Mac: Xcode -- https://developer.apple.com/xcode/
#
# Source Example:
# 	1. http://www.cs.columbia.edu/~sable/summer2000/ttt.c
#
# Building/Execution:
# 	1. Compile: gcc -o TTT TTT.c
#	2. Run: TTT.exe OR ./TTT
#
# (Note: C++ code will have .cpp for source and is built with g++ inplace of gcc)

###############################################################################
